have you tested your ssh key setup, fire wall, and switch settings to ensure all nodes are talking to each other?<br><br><div class="gmail_quote"><div><div></div><div class="h5">On Mon, Dec 27, 2010 at 1:07 AM, Advanced Computing Group University of Padova <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:acg.unipd@gmail.com" target="_blank">acg.unipd@gmail.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>


